item.title: About
item.description: Hello! I’m Mert Okan Deliktaş, a student at Yeditepe University with a strong focus on cybersecurity, networking, and IT industry. My passion for technology drives me to constantly learn and develop skills in these fields. I enjoy exploring the latest threats in cybersecurity, understanding network security, and discovering the dynamics of the IT industry. My goal is to continue growing my expertise and contribute to the field in the future
